| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4748 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a4aeabaa-ebe1-5d81-be83-289d0d60dd95"
